cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "audit-the-judge: Auditing the LLM-as-Judge with Paired Synthetic Controls"
abstract: >-
  A framework that calibrates an LLM-as-judge before its verdicts are trusted, using
  paired synthetic controls (a negative control on equivalent answers plus positive
  controls that inject known position and length biases), bootstrap confidence
  intervals, and Benjamini-Hochberg FDR correction.
type: software
authors:
